Maintainer: Domenico Vistocco <domenico.vistocco@unina.it>
Description: DESPOTA is a novel approach exploiting permutation test to automatically detect a partition among those embedded in a dendrogram. Unlike the traditional approach, DESPOTA includes partitions not corresponding to horizontal cuts of the dendrogram in the search space. Reference in Bruzzese D., Vistocco D. (2015) <https://doi.org/10.1007/s00357-015-9179-x> .
